1. *Ministar* je posetio gradilište nove bolnice. (The minister visited the construction site of the new hospital.)
2. Predsednik je imenovao novog *ministra* spoljnih poslova. (The president appointed a new minister of foreign affairs.)
3. *Ministarka* je obećala da će se boriti protiv korupcije. (The female minister promised to fight against corruption.)
4. Naša zemlja ima 16 različitih *ministarstava*. (Our country has 16 different ministries.)
5. *Ministru* je upućena molba da razmotri mogućnost povećanja budžeta za kulturu. (The minister was sent a request to consider the possibility of increasing the budget for culture.)
6. U vladi su se pojavile glasine o smeni *ministra*. (Rumors have surfaced in the government about the dismissal of a minister.)
7. *Ministri* su se sastali da bi razgovarali o novom zakonu. (The ministers met to discuss a new law.)
8. *Ministarki* su upućene pohvale za uspešnu realizaciju projekta. (Praises were directed to the female minister for the successful implementation of the project.)
9. *Ministarstvo* finansija je objavilo novu poresku politiku. (The Ministry of Finance has announced a new tax policy.)
10. Nakon nekoliko meseci na funkciji, *ministar* je podneo ostavku. (After several months in office, the minister resigned.)